rows.label: qst004004_msg0002
rows.name:
Come to think of it... this is
just an Armu rumor, so it might
not be reliable, but...

rows.label: qst004004_msg0004
rows.name:
The mama Armus were chatting
about some mischievous
Tirkin showing up, mo.

rows.label: qst004004_msg0005
rows.name:
But if Tirkin entered the town,
there'd be a huge uproar, mo.

rows.label: qst004004_msg0006
rows.name:
I haven't heard about any uproar,
so it's probably unrelated, mo.

rows.label: qst004004_msg0101
rows.name:
How do I know what the
Armus are saying?

rows.label: qst004004_msg0102
rows.name:
Oyoyo has been raising
Armus for 40 years, mo.

rows.label: qst004004_msg0103
rows.name:
Understanding what they're
saying is a piece of cake, mo.
